  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Your Skills and Interests\r\n\r\n###Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Share with the chatbot about your skills and interests.\r\n\r\n:::details [Use these sentence starters from your Unit Guide]\r\n- I like to spend time...\r\n- I'm happiest when...\r\n- I'm most confident when...\r\n- I like learning about...\r\n- Some other skills I have are...\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n2. When you feel like you've shared enough about yourself, prompt the chatbot with the following:\r\n\r\n> Based on what I've shared, would you recommend I explore careers related to People, Things, or Ideas? Explain why.",
